<div class="hero-text" style="background-image:url('<%= image_path 'Sola_5000_Banner.jpg' %>')">
  <div class="text">
    <h1>Celebrating 5,000 Stylists &amp;<br>Salon Professionals Nationwide</h1>
    <h3>Click to watch video</h3>
    <a href="//www.youtube.com/watch?v=b9Ocv4vfvqc" class="play-button"></a>
  </div>
  <div class="learn-more">
    <h3>Learn More</h3>
    <span class="ss-navigatedown"></span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row text-center">

    <h4 style="margin: 50px auto 35px auto">We're celebrating an exciting milestone, and we want to thank YOU for being a part of it. We now have more than 5,000 stylists and salon professionals running their own salons, none of which would be possible without the wonderful support from the professional beauty industry and the confidence and trust from each and every stylist.<br><br>
    Each member of our community has an exciting story to tell and a unique journey that has led them to where they are today. Founded in 2004, Sola provides an upscale, professional setting for stylists to take control of their careers, putting ownership, freedom, and a better work-life balance at their fingertips. With more than 225 locations, Sola is proud to empower each stylist to live their best life. So join our Solabrationâ€“celebrating the success of 5,000+ entrepreneurs nationwide!</h4>

    <h1 style="color:#EC008C;margin-bottom: 5px;">5,000+ Salon Professionals. 225+ Locations.</h1>

    <h1 style="color:#499CD3;margin-bottom: 40px;">Thank you for being a part of this exciting milestone!</h1>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="callout blue">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h1 style="margin-top:0">The Faces of Sola</h1>
    <h3>Click on an image to read their stories</h3>
  </div>
</div>

<%= render 'shared/carousels/sola_spotlight' %>

<div class="container text-center">
  <div class="row">
    <h3 style="margin: 25px auto 30px auto;">Sola 5000 Gallery</h3>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container image-grid">
  <% (1..84).each do |i| %>
    <div class="three columns <%= 'more' if i > 16 %>"><a rel="sola5000" href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/solasalonstudios/5000/<%= i %>.jpg"><%= image_tag "https://s3.amazonaws.com/solasalonstudios/5000/#{i}.jpg" %></a></div>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="callout blue" style="margin-top:1px">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <button class="button inverted view-more" style="margin-bottom: 0;">View More</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="padding:90px 0 75px 0;background:#fcfcfc;border-top:1px solid #EFEEEE;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="one-half column">
        <%= link_to 'Join our community', :contact_us, :class => 'button primary block' %>
      </div>
      <div class="one-half column">
        <%= link_to 'Partner with us', '#', :class => 'button primary block partner-button' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="partner-modal modal-content">
  <h4 style="margin-bottom:15px;">Partner With Us</h4>
  <p style="margin-bottom:30px">Interested in partnering with Sola Salon Studios? Tell us a little bit about your company, brand or product and we will be in touch!</p>
  <%= form_tag :partner_inquiry, :id => 'partner_inquiry' do %>
    <input type="text" name="subject" placeholder="Subject" />
    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Full Name" />
    <input type="text" name="company_name" placeholder="Company Name" />
    <input type="text" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" />
    <input type="text" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number" />
    <textarea name="message" placeholder="Leave a Message"></textarea>
    <button class="primary block">Submit Request</button>
  <% end %>
</div>


